did.unittitle: Prints and Printing Lantern Slide Collection
did.abstract: Collection consists of black and white glass lantern slides of prints and printing techniques worldwide.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: The materials are open for research.

userestrict.head: Conditions Governing Use
userestrict.p: Copyright has not been transferred to Yale University. Further use of this material may be subject to the copyright laws of the United States (Title 17, United States Code) or to site license or other rights management terms or conditions.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Prints and Printing Lantern Slide Collection, Arts Library, Yale University

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Collection consists of black and white glass lantern slides of prints and printing techniques worldwide.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: Arranged alphabetically by geographical region or country. Further arranged by individual artist name. Individual artist name sections may be preceded by an Anonymous or Miscellaneous grouping. Preliminary section on printing techniques (lettering and printed books).
